data.description: This beautiful Highlands Ranch home checks so many boxes * Big floor plan with vaulted ceilings * High windows that let in lots of light * Four bedrooms upstairs * Dedicated home office * Great big family room * Space for your big screen and your oversized sectional sofa * Smart fridge with touch screen and Wi-Fi * Gorgeous stainless convection double oven * Smart convection microwave with barcode scanner * Spacious master with 5-piece bath * Luxurious new carpeting * New window blinds * Custom crystal chandeliers * Marquis Wish seven-guest hot tub * Flowing backyard water feature with koi pond * Brand New AC in Oct 2023 * Newer furnace * Newer water heater * Humidifier * So many family friendly amenities are at your doorstep * Schools * Walking and bike trails * Beautiful Civic Green Park * Tons of shopping * Highlands Ranch Town Center * If you’ve been fantasizing about the prefect Highlands Ranch lifestyle, your fantasy is about to become reality. Incredible square footage for this price!
